{"tid":1726811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誇行提款罰中資","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T09:16:49.000Z","uid":185013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7669bef39663f1ec4c905f821f3f223b337586e8","tid":1726811,"uid":185013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"去中資銀行開戶口<br />\n保持低存款或零存款<br />\n每人每天用jetco 銀通提款一次款<br />\n去非中資如渣打（英資）或東亞（港資）提款<br />\n假設每次交易費為5元<br />\n每月30次x$5/次＝$150<br />\n1萬人就150萬<br />\n10萬人就1500萬<br />\n<br />\n去盡啲仲可以<br />\n1. 提款前先用FPS 轉錢入戶口<br />\n即刻去提款<br />\n(連過夜息都唔比佢賺) <br />\n2. 一天提款多次<br />\n<br />\n#黃色經濟圈<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\nRef:<br />\n<a href=\"https://is.gd/bIJE6W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FbIJE6W&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=514d7c42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/bIJE6W</a>"},{"pid":"091cfd2012ef8e27dcb4997182fb544b5092d1ee","tid":1726811,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:16:49.000Z","msg":"我地要做既係美國戰線阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地藍屍撐由佢地，佢係係咪都奶共架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大件事 唔好玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國會美中經濟與安全審議委員會發表年度報告，表示若果中國對香港出動解放軍或武警干預香港局勢，美國國會應該撤銷《美國-香港政策法》給予香港獨立關稅區的特殊地位。"}]}